{"tid":2235883,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"市傳AMD以300億美元收購晶片巨頭Xilinx賽靈思","createTime":"2020-10-09T04:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T05:36:06.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"79c92147b3b3f46ad0b43d47bb9d1669e55bf635","tid":2235883,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T04:55:25.000Z","msg":"〔財經頻道／綜合報導〕英特爾（Intel）多年來掌握資料中心伺服器市場，現在已有越來越多同業欲藉著併購來衝擊英特爾地位，如輝達（Nvidia）已收購Mellanox、洽談安謀（Arm）中。新消息傳出，超微半導體（AMD）將出價高達300億美元（約新台幣8587.3億元）買下晶片巨頭賽靈思（Xilinx）。<br />\n<br />\n《彭博》報導，知情人士透露情況仍在不斷變化，但交易可能最早在下週就能達成。AMD和賽靈思的代表拒絕對此評論。<br />\n<br />\n.....<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3316303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3316303&d=bW%2FimIc%2BBhL52Hx1BZusr%2BgAExyYYV7WT87CuOwwBqU%3D&h=317da5b5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fec.ltn.com.tw%2Fm%2Farticle%2Fbreakingnews%2F3316303&h=94f96194\" target=\"_blank\">https://ec.ltn.com.tw/m/article/breakingnews/3316303</a>"},{"pid":"3266ad86d63f038f442312d9dea46c5e1cb8fe24","tid":2235883,"uid":32352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:01:09.000Z","msg":"整fpga?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae5ebf4f60381e4b5579857f98574d5dae21309a","tid":2235883,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:12:05.000Z","msg":"煙條下去吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b23f53e3e27afae8c4d204e50f50b9dcd185e83","tid":2235883,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T05:16:02.000Z","msg":"amd<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree